(ns farsund.window.fx
  (:require [cljs.spec.alpha :as s]
            [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [taoensso.encore :as e]
            [oops.core :refer [oget]]
            [goog.events :as events]))


(s/def ::event (s/and vector? #(keyword? (first %))))

(s/def ::dispatch ::event)
(s/def ::debounce-ms int?)
(s/def ::id keyword?)
(s/def ::on-resize-args (s/keys :req-un [::dispatch] :opt-un [::debounce-ms ::id]))
(s/def ::on-scroll-args (s/keys :req-un [::dispatch] :opt-un [::debounce-ms ::id]))


(def listeners_ (atom {}))


(defn- setup-listener! [event-type callback id]
  (let [key (events/listen js/window event-type (if (fn? callback)
                                                  callback
                                                  #(rf/dispatch callback)))]
    (when id
      (swap! listeners_ assoc-in [event-type id] key))))


(defn- stop-listener! [event-type id]
  (when-let [key (get-in @listeners_ [event-type id])]
    (events/unlistenByKey key)
    (swap! listeners_ update event-type #(dissoc % id))))


(defn get-window-size []
  {:inner-width  (oget js/window :innerWidth)
   :inner-height (oget js/window :innerHeight)
   :client-height (oget (.querySelector js/document "html") :clientHeight)})


(defn on-resize [{:keys [dispatch debounce-ms]}]
  (let [r (get-window-size)]
    (js/setTimeout #(rf/dispatch (conj dispatch r)) (or debounce-ms 166))))


(defn get-window-scroll []
  {:scroll-top    (oget (.querySelector js/document "html") :scrollTop)
   :scroll-height (oget (.querySelector js/document "html") :scrollHeight)})


(defn on-scroll [{:keys [dispatch debounce-ms]}]
  (let [r (get-window-scroll)]
    (js/setTimeout #(rf/dispatch (conj dispatch r)) (or debounce-ms 166))))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/on-resize
  (fn [coll]
    (doseq [{:keys [id] :as config} coll]
      (s/assert ::on-resize-args config)
      (setup-listener! events/EventType.RESIZE (partial on-resize config) id))))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/init-window
  (fn [coll]
    (doseq [dispatch coll]
      (s/assert ::event dispatch)
      (rf/dispatch (conj dispatch (merge (get-window-size) (get-window-scroll)))))))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/stop-on-resize
  (fn [{:keys [id]}]
    (stop-listener! events/EventType.RESIZE id)))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/on-scroll
  (fn [coll]
    (doseq [{:keys [id] :as config} coll]
      (s/assert ::on-scroll-args config)
      ;(on-scroll config)
      (setup-listener! events/EventType.SCROLL (partial on-scroll config) id))))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/update-scroll-height
  (fn [_]
    (e/swap-in! re-frame.db/app-db [:window :scroll-height] (oget (.querySelector js/document "html") :scrollHeight))))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/stop-on-scroll
  (fn [{:keys [id]}]
    (stop-listener! events/EventType.SCROLL id)))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/on-focus
  (fn [{:keys [dispatch id]}]
    (setup-listener! events/EventType.FOCUS dispatch id)))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/stop-on-focus
  (fn [{:keys [id]}]
    (stop-listener! events/EventType.FOCUS id)))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/on-blur
  (fn [{:keys [dispatch id]}]
    (setup-listener! events/EventType.BLUR dispatch id)))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/stop-on-blur
  (fn [{:keys [id]}]
    (stop-listener! events/EventType.BLUR id)))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/on-hashchange
  (fn [{:keys [dispatch id]}]
    (setup-listener! events/EventType.HASHCHANGE dispatch id)))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/stop-on-hashchange
  (fn [{:keys [id]}]
    (stop-listener! events/EventType.HASHCHANGE id)))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/scroll-smooth
  (fn [y]
    (.scroll js/window (clj->js {:top      y
                                 :behavior "smooth"}))))


(rf/reg-fx
  :window/scroll-to
  (fn [[x y]]
    (.scrollTo js/window x y)))
